    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a showroom-quality find. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining a deep, factory-fresh shine with no chips, scratches, or imperfections of any kind. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with the leather upholstery and trim appearing as if they've never been used. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership.",
