      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for daily commuting. While the engine and transmission are in good working order and have been regularly serviced, the exterior shows some noticeable scratches and minor dings consistent with its age. Inside, the upholstery is intact but displays some fading and signs of use. It is a solid, functional car that provides dependable transportation for a budget-conscious buyer.",
