    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride that won't break the bank? This car is in fair condition and has plenty of life left in it! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its time on the road, it remains a solid, functional choice for anyone needing reliable transportation with a bit of personality. It's ready to get you where you need to go!",
