      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Demonstrating consistent mechanical integrity and a refined aesthetic, it offers a balanced synthesis of proven performance and long-term reliability. We invite you to experience the superior handling and well-preserved interior that distinguish this exceptional example within its class.",
