    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for all my commutes and weekend trips. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with a new owner today! If you\u2019re looking for a reliable car that still looks great and drives smooth, this is definitely the one for you. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by for a test drive!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
