    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver\u2019s specimen featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to the rear wheels via the M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis remains taut, with the rear subframe reinforced and the VANOS system recently serviced to ensure precise cam timing. Suspension geometry is true, utilizing MacPherson struts and a multi-link rear setup for superior lateral acceleration. While the aesthetic reflects honest use, the mechanical vitals are robust, providing the visceral, analog feedback expected of this platform's longitudinal front-engine, rear-drive layout.",
