    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes a perfect balance between performance and practicality, presenting in well-maintained condition throughout. The exterior retains a high-gloss luster, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, professional touch-up on the rear bumper\u2014typical of a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. The alloy wheels are clean with no significant curb rash, wrapped in tires with plenty of tread remaining. Inside, the smoke-free cabin remains inviting; the upholstery shows only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster, while the carpets have been protected by all-weather mats since day one. Every feature, including the panoramic sunroof, navigation system, and heated seats, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is robust. It has followed a strict maintenance schedule, with a recent fluid service and brake inspection already completed. The engine pulls strongly without hesitation, and the transmission delivers smooth, predictable shifts. This is a solid, reliable example ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
